About Us
First-Rate RV Park in Perry
Are you looking to head out in the wilderness for the adventure of a lifetime? If so, you owe it to yourself to visit Tide and Timber Rv Park, located 12 miles south of Perry, Florida. Nestled amongst pines and oaks, you'll find plenty of relaxing time around the fire. Just 1/2 mile to the Gulf of Mexico with ...

A Little Piece of Paradise
We understand that while some people love the great outdoors and want to be disconnected from comfort and convenience, others want the possibility of getting out of the city but still being able to use social media. Boats & Fishing
Fishing is abundant in the area, and we have room, so bring your boat. No boat? Find a Captain in Keaton or nearby Steinhatchee to enjoy a great day on the water for fishing or scalloping (in season).
